data.description: Welcome Home!  If you are looking for privacy your search is over!  This unique 3 bedroom, 3 full bath home is nestled on over 10 private ACRES on Fine Creek.  The open floor plan features a Living Room / Kitchen Combo separated by an Island, an upstairs or a downstairs primary bedroom, and a huge unfinished walk-out basement for lots of storage or even finishing off for more living space.  The updated Kitchen features granite countertops, tile backsplash, stainless wall oven, microwave, trash compactor, dishwasher, stainless farm sink, and new LVP flooring.  All bathrooms have been updated and are stunning!  Heated tile flooring in hallway and laundry room.  Side load 1-car Garage.  Don't let this one get away. Only 10 minutes from VA-288.  There's still time to make this your new HOME for the HOLIDAYS!
